#

Instant Pot Borscht

40 min
$10
220 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Soup

Tags:

souphealthyquick

Description

A vibrant, hearty beet soup that's quick to prepare in the Instant Pot, packed with vegetables and a touch of sour cream for creaminess.

Ingredients

  • beets: 4 medium, peeled and diced
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrots: 2, peeled and diced
  • potatoes: 2 medium, peeled and diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • sour cream: for serving
  • fresh dill: for garnish
